Repeater Widget Considerations

To facet repeater widget data, use a query with a grouping. 
Changing the mode in a query used by a repeater widget can cause errors.
If a dashboard uses multiple layouts, changes made to a repeater widget are shown in all layouts.
When adding one-click actions, include the dataset row identifier.
You canâ€™t select a border color for a text widget in a repeater when setting a conditional formatting rule that applies to the field only.
